scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Karan utilized a numbering systems of fractions (a fractional system) to organize the bulk of his fieldwork photos for Bhutan and Sikkim. This subseries is arranged by the numerator of the fraction first, then by the denominator second. Photos come in both 3 inch by 4 inch contact prints and 9.5 inch by 12 inch full prints. Neither format is comprehensive; reviewing both groups will provide the most complete set of photos.
